p%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=2017368288689466264fdf47_78275456"/><published>2025-08-07T14:57:17+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>3157f8792645f5ded623c3219499dabc</id><title>(511)TVB贏左!股價爆升! 呢條片，張潤衡咪唔小心認左自己當日有食煙囉!</title><updated>2025-08-07T14:59:54+08:00</updated><author><name>劉穎鏇</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-07T14:59:54+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573513114"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573513114"&gt;1:20:00&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;張潤衡：我阿爸睇新聞見到話我喺山上食煙，嬲到摑左我一巴&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;主持人問佢：你爸爸知你有食煙既習慣？&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;張潤衡答：我冇食煙既習慣啊，&lt;span style="color: #ff0000; "&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;嗰次係我第二次攞起支煙&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ff0000; "&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9"&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen="" class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/NdkGHtCmv5E?wmode=transparent" wmode="Opaque"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?app=desktop&amp;amp;v=NdkGHtCmv5E" target="_blank"&gt;7月3日 壹錘定音&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a class="postmorevideochannel" href="videochannel.php" title="進入香討影片區"&gt;進入香討影片區&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32001342&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=2017368288689466264fdf47_78275456"/><published>2025-08-07T14:59:54+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>1e51e5778578501b8beec5c0a685be24</id><title>港元定存｜港元半年定存最高險守兩厘 兩間中小行逆市加息</title><updated>2025-08-07T15:31:25+08:00</updated><author><name>katewells</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-07T15:31:25+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573513402"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573513402"&gt;港滙再觸7.85，在劈息潮下昨罕現逆市加息，扭轉8月開局至今有減無加的慘況，適逢本周兩天共走資逾148億元。可惜，今天（8月7日）未見港銀明顯大舉迎戰反擊，暫有7間銀行調整港元定期存款息，當中4減兩加，另天星（AirStar Bank）則加減不一。減息包括素來打高息牌的富邦，自7月中以來巳3度削息，新近更撤兩厘息，是繼天星、理慧（livi bank）及大眾財務以來，近日第4間的定存息回落至「1字頭」。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://inews.hket.com/article/3989999/%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83%E5%AE%9A%E5%AD%98%EF%BD%9C%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%AE%9A%E5%AD%98%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E9%9A%AA%E5%AE%88%E5%85%A9%E5%8E%98%E3%80%80%E5%85%A9%E9%96%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%8F%E8%A1%8C%E9%80%86%E5%B8%82%E5%8A%A0%E6%81%AF%C2%A0" target="_blank" uhash="fb9c037a7f082d1ecc13e4f6a106b097"&gt;港元定存｜港元半年定存最高險守兩厘兩間中小行逆市加息&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32001360&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=2017368288689466264fdf47_78275456"/><published>2025-08-07T15:31:25+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>d2621fac9ce53c8f523a180c9cf51dba</id><title>淡友死心啦</title><updated>2025-08-07T15:38:39+08:00</updated><author><name>版煮報夢.</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-07T15:38:39+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573513486"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573513486"&gt;人造市你輸硬，夠膽你就高位追貨 夠膽你就熊，擺明食硬你&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="46" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_30.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32001369&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&am